    "description": "Side-by-side comparison of ClickHouse services: query rates, memory, connections and rows, series keyed by service_name. Panels adapted as a reference from the ClickHouse mix-in (Grafana dashboard 23415, github.com/ClickHouse/clickhouse-mixin, commit c54f56e0). Rebuilt on PMM's Apache-2.0 dashboard shell.",
